<h1>Delete Account – Mom’sNest</h1>

<p>
Mom’sNest respects your privacy. You can request deletion of your account and associated data at any time.
</p>

<h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>
<ol>
    <li>Send an email to <b>support@momsnest.app</b></li>
    <li>Use the subject line: <b>Account Deletion Request</b></li>
    <li>Mention your registered email or phone number</li>
</ol>

<h2>What Data Is Deleted</h2>
<ul>
    <li>User profile information</li>
    <li>Authentication details</li>
    <li>Saved preferences and app data</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Retention</h2>
<p>
Some anonymized or legally required data (such as transaction or audit logs) may be retained for up to
<b>30 days</b> for compliance purposes and then permanently deleted.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>
If you have any questions, contact us at <b>mayankraj902@gmail.com</b>
</p>

